g src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbbebfb0cd89396a4c1924b79bdfd9a0e7e3ae9","tid":912742,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:51:18.000Z","msg":"劉小麗點睇佢老友劉細良太平紳士牽涉偽造訪問害人？"},{"pid":"9577db42646f4604a2c50f24d442cb135f098b88","tid":912742,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:54:52.000Z","msg":"放人做臥底攞料同入去之後亂寫係2回事喎，大公呢個差不多係寫小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee2088f03fed9d6342700d14007b109ad531fdf","tid":912742,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T03:00:42.000Z","msg":"記乜者<br />\n全職五毛而已<br />\n呢d pk等大陸一缺水自然就失業<br />\n將來想轉行?<br />\n小姐你邊到做話?<br />\n大公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返去等消息啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}